// on november of 2020 the huricanes Eta and Iota striked Guatemala and Central America
//This scprit analize the flooding during this event in Quiche, Guatemala
// using Copernicus Sentinel 2 images from 2020-03-01 to 2020-11-30
// link to the GEE Script: https://code.earthengine.google.com/c0027e9af8e41f35cd857d19529caf6f
